## Status Words

| Status | Meaning | Action Required |
|--------|---------|----------------|
| DONE | Task completed, verified working | None |
| VERIFIED | Code compiles, tests pass, manual check done | None |
| BLOCKED | Cannot proceed, dependency missing or blocked | Escalate to orchestrator |
| NEEDS_REVIEW | Changes ready for human review | Flag for PR review |
| DEPRECATED | Old pattern, use new approach instead | Update callers |
| ARCH_BOUNDARY_VIOLATION | Violates Three-Layer Intelligence Stack | Fix immediately, escalate |
| SECURITY_SENSITIVE | Involves auth, API keys, PII | Extra review required |

